f%20Christian%20Flanders%20sitting%20at%20his%20trading%20desk.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ec5460ce3009a0fac7ab87%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22765%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EChristian%20Flanders%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChristian%20Flanders%20is%20leading%20his%20division%20in%20the%20US%20Investing%20Championship%20with%20a%20253%25%20year-to-date%20return.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20uses%20the%20so-called%20episodic%20pivot%20trading%20strategy%20to%20ride%20the%20momentum%20of%20rising%20stocks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFlanders%20outlines%20how%20he%20picks%20stocks%20to%20trade%2C%20and%20when%20he%20gets%20in%20and%20out.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20natural%20human%20instincts%20you%20have%2C%20you%20have%20to%20do%20the%20complete%20opposite%20in%20almost%20every%20circumstance%20to%20be%20a%20successful%20trader%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Christian%20Flanders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20Flanders%20was%20a%20trading%20assistant%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-a-bond%23%3A~%3Atext%3DA%2520bond%2520is%2520a%2520loan%2520you%2520make%2520to%2520a%2520company%2Ccome%2520along%2520with%2520ownership%2520rights.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebond-trading%3C%2Fa%3E%20firm%20by%20day%20and%20a%20professional%20online%20poker%20player%20by%20night.%20Both%20occupations%20served%20as%20meaningful%20sources%20of%20income%20for%20him%20%E2%80%94%20that%20is%20until%20the%202008%20financial%20crisis%20closed%20down%20his%20firm%2C%20and%20eventually%20regulation%20shut%20down%20many%20poker%20sites%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%202017%2C%20he%20decided%20he%20had%20to%20pivot%20and%20elected%20to%20give%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fstock-trading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estock%20trading%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20try.%20His%20appetite%20for%20risk%20and%20uncertainty%20made%20for%20a%20smooth%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20actually%20started%20off%20well%2C%20which%20is%20probably%20worse%20in%20some%20ways%20than%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20Flanders%20said%20of%20those%20early%20days.%20He%20recalls%20generating%20gains%20of%20nearly%2050%25%20by%20the%20end%20of%202017%2C%20performance%20that%20set%20him%20up%20for%20unrealistic%20expectations%20and%2C%20eventually%2C%20disappointment.%20The%20following%20year%2C%20he%20saw%20most%20of%20those%20gains%20quickly%20evaporate%20after%20a%20series%20of%20bad%20bets%20he%20made%20from%20chasing%20hype.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20shorting%20volatility%20had%20been%20all%20the%20hype.%20Flanders%20recalled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-target-manager-becomes-millionaire-using-short-volatility-trade-2017-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereading%20a%20story%20about%20a%20Target%20employee%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20became%20a%20millionaire%2C%20going%20from%20%24500%2C000%20to%20%2412%20million%20in%20five%20years%20after%20shorting%20the%20CBOE%20Volatility%20Index%20%E2%80%94%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fvix%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVIX%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20ultimately%20amounted%20to%20a%20bet%20that%20the%20stock%20market%20would%20stay%20placid%2C%20with%20interest%20rates%20having%20been%20near%20zero%20for%20so%20long.%20Excited%20about%20the%20prospect%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20replicate%20the%20success%20by%20buying%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fproshares-short-vix-short-term-futures-etf-us74347w1302%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProShares%20Short%20VIX%20Short-Term%20Futures%20ETF%3C%2Fa%3E%20(SVXY)%2C%20an%20inverse%20ETF%20that%20shorts%20the%20VIX.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20February%205%2C%202018%2C%20he%20bought%20multiple%20shares%20of%20SVXY%20totaling%203%2C000%20at%20an%20average%20split-adjusted%20price%20of%20%2467.%20It%20had%20been%20on%20a%20strong%20uptrend%20over%20the%20previous%20two%20years.%20The%20fund%20was%20down%20sharply%20that%20week.%20Flanders%20saw%20it%20as%20a%20chance%20to%20get%20in%20cheap%20with%20the%20assumption%20it%20would%20recover.%20But%20it%20never%20did.%20He%20sold%20at%20an%20average%20split-adjusted%20price%20of%20%2435%2C%20according%20to%20his%20brokerage%20statement.%20That's%20when%20he%20learned%20his%20biggest%20lesson%3A%20that%20managing%20his%20emotions%20was%2095%25%20of%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20emotions%20are%20going%20to%20make%20you%20do%20the%20wrong%20thing%20at%20exactly%20the%20worst%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Flanders%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20panic-sell%20at%20the%20lows%3B%20you're%20going%20to%20panic-buy%20at%20the%20highs.%20You're%20going%20to%20trade%20when%20the%20stock%20is%20zigging%20and%20zagging%20and%20get%20chopped%20up.%20When%20the%20stock%20finally%20breaks%20out%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20short%20it.%20When%20the%20stock%20finally%20breaks%20down%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20buy%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20realized%20that%20a%20combination%20of%20sticking%20to%20a%20strict%20rules-based%20process%20that%20involved%20filtering%20the%20right%20stocks%2C%20trading%20the%20same%20patterns%2C%20and%20setting%20stop%20losses%20was%20the%20only%20way%20he%20could%20manage%20his%20reactions.%20This%20way%2C%20he%20wasn't%20making%20decisions%20on%20the%20fly.%20After%20years%20of%20honing%20his%20approach%2C%20in%202024%20he%20decided%20to%20put%20his%20skills%20to%20the%20test%20in%20the%20US%20Investing%20Championship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20August%2C%20he's%20in%20the%20lead%20for%20his%20division%2C%20up%20by%20253%25%2C%20according%20to%20the%20competition's%20founder%2C%20Norman%20Zadeh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2233bd288f-93ed-440f-936d-9cddf2aed247%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrading%20on%20episodic%20pivots%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Flanders%20was%20honing%20his%20skills%2C%20he%20watched%20numerous%20interviews%20of%20other%20traders%20who%20shared%20their%20strategies.%20One%20pattern%20trade%20in%20particular%20grabbed%20his%20attention%3A%20the%20episodic%20pivot%2C%20which%20happens%20when%20a%20catalyst%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20positive%20news%20or%20earnings%20%E2%80%94%20leads%20to%20a%20sudden%20shift%20or%20move%20in%20a%20stock's%20price.%20The%20theory%20behind%20the%20episodic%20pivot%20is%20that%20this%20initial%20move%20higher%20%E2%80%94%20also%20known%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bgap%20up%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20will%20retain%20momentum%20and%20continue%20to%20deliver%20gains.%20That%20expectation%20of%20further%20upside%20rationalizes%20the%20decision%20to%20buy%20when%20a%20stock%20or%20security%20has%20already%20seen%20a%20sizable%20jump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20chart%2C%20it%20can%20often%20look%20like%20a%20wide%20space%20between%20two%20candles%20after%20the%20stock's%20price%20opens%20significantly%20higher%20than%20where%20it%20was%20in%20premarket%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20like%2C%20wow%2C%20I've%20seen%20these%20trades%20before.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20I%20was%20too%20gun%20shy%20to%20take%20them%20because%20when%20a%20stock%20is%20gapping%20up%2030%25%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20buying%20it%20is%20very%20unnatural%20for%20something%20that's%20up%20that%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20Flanders%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20not%20all%20gap-ups%20on%20a%20chart%20are%20a%20buy%20signal.%20After%20all%2C%20if%20a%20stock%20has%20already%20risen%20so%20much%2C%20its%20upside%20may%20be%20capped.%20Flanders%20learned%20that%20the%20hard%20way%20after%20piling%20into%20a%20few%20that%20crashed.%20He%20was%20eventually%20able%20to%20pinpoint%20his%20main%20mistake%3A%20the%20stocks%20he%20was%20targeting%20had%20weak%20fundamentals%20and%20volume.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20started%20breaking%20out%20and%20I%20bought%20them%20aggressively%20and%20they%20all%20failed.%20And%20I%20just%20kept%20getting%20stopped%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Flanders%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20he%20crafted%20a%20process%20that%20would%20help%20him%20avoid%20these%20sorts%20of%20unsustainable%20share%20pops.%20One%20of%20the%20things%20he%20did%20was%20avoid%20trading%20less%20liquid%20stocks%20such%20as%20smaller-caps%20that%20aren't%20as%20well-followed.%20Instead%2C%20Flanders%20says%20he%20sticks%20to%20stocks%20with%20higher%20institutional%20ownership%20that%20are%20near%20or%20at%20their%20all-time%20highs%20and%20have%20recently%20consolidated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20mind%2C%20these%20indicators%20suggest%20that%20demand%20is%20sustainably%20strong%20even%20when%20there's%20selling%20pressure.%20It%20reduces%20the%20chances%20that%20the%20stock's%20rally%20is%20short-lived%2C%20an%20outcome%20that%20could%20cause%20traders%20to%20get%20trapped%20holding%20the%20bag%20if%20it%20reverses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELarge%20volume%20should%20accompany%20this%20demand%2C%20ideally%2C%20the%20most%20the%20stocks%20has%20ever%20had%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20goal%20is%20to%20buy%20a%20stock%20and%20sell%20at%20a%20higher%20price.%20To%20do%20that%2C%20you%20need%20to%20find%20stocks%20that%20are%20in%20high%20demand%20where%20people%20want%20the%20stock%20and%20they're%20willing%20to%20bid%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Flanders%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c206acb7-21ba-47d7-8887-5f482c2b1f15%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinding%20the%20trade%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20thing%20Flanders%20does%20on%20a%20given%20day%20is%20check%20his%20scanner%20for%20the%20top%20movers%20of%20the%20day%20during%20pre-market%20hours.%20He%20then%20singles%20out%20tickers%20that%20are%20up%20by%2010%25%20and%20trading%20above%20%2410%20with%20an%20average%20daily%20volume%20above%20half%20a%20million%20shares.%20Then%20he%20checks%20the%20news%20to%20confirm%20that%20they%20have%20a%20strong%20catalyst.%20On%20most%20days%2C%20there%20aren't%20any%20stocks%2C%20on%20some%20days%20there%20could%20be%20a%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20he%20finds%20a%20stock%20that%20meets%20his%20criteria%2C%20he%20reviews%20its%2012-month%20chart%20to%20confirm%20it%20has%20been%20on%20a%20strong%20uptrend%2C%20up%20by%20a%20minimum%20of%20100%25%20from%20its%2052-week%20low%20before%20consolidating%20for%20a%20minimum%20of%207%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20call%20it%20trading%2C%20but%20it's%20really%20waiting%20because%2095%25%20of%20the%20time%20you%20don't%20do%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20Flanders%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20he%20decides%20to%20take%20a%20trade%2C%20he%20will%20buy%20the%20stock%20at%20the%20open.%20His%20initial%20stop-loss%20order%20is%20often%20set%205%25%20below%20his%20entry%20price.%20If%20the%20stock%20moves%20up%2C%20he%20will%20take%20some%20gains.%20His%20stop-loss%20will%20then%20move%20up%2C%20trailing%20the%2010-day%20moving%20average%2C%20allowing%20him%20to%20ride%20the%20rally%20for%20weeks%20until%20he%20stops%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20strategy%20has%20a%20low%20win%20ratio%2C%20at%20about%2030%25%2C%20because%20the%20volatility%20will%20often%20stop%20him%20out.%20However%2C%20on%20average%20he%20says%20his%20gains%20are%20five%20times%20as%20big%20as%20his%20losses.%20This%20is%20because%20his%20stop%20loss%20limits%20the%20amount%20he%20can%20lose%20while%20allowing%20him%20to%20rid%20the%20stock%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a0a17f09-01ae-47c7-8333-eb408ff53ce3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrade%20example%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2018%2C%20IT%20Solutions%20Provider%20Super%20Micro%20Computer's%20(SMCI)%20met%20all%20the%20characteristics%20outlined%20above.%20It%20had%20an%20earnings%20report%20after%20the%20closing%20bell%20that%20was%20the%20type%20of%20event%20capable%20of%20generating%20a%20gap-up.%20The%20stock%20was%20also%20coming%20off%20a%20strong%2012-month%20upt