er-business-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726827961000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66de902d5444ffafa7638b4d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-cuban-says-trump-most-unethical-person-ever-business-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Billionaire%20Mark%20Cuban%20accused%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20of%20lacking%20character%2C%20continuing%20his%20recent%20criticism%20of%20the%202024%20GOP%20candidate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22esnodgrass%40businessinsider.com%20(Erin%20Snodgrass%2CAditi%20Bharade%2CCheryl%20Teh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-cuban-says-trump-most-unethical-person-ever-business-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tirupati%20Laddoo%20Row%20Reaches%20Top%20Court%20For%20%26quot%3BProtecting%20Religious%20Rights%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20row%20over%20animal%20fat%20allegedly%20being%20used%20to%20make%20the%20famed%20Tirupati%20laddoos%20reached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%20with%20a%20lawyer%20filing%20a%20petition%20alleging%20that%20the%20act%20violates%20fundamental%20Hindu%20religious%20customs%20and%20deeply%20hurts%20the%20sentiments%20of%20countless%20devotees%20who%20consider%20the%20'prasad'%20a%20sacred%20blessing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20has%20said%20the%20alleged%20presence%20of%20animal%20fat%20in%20the%20laddoos%20is%20symptomatic%20of%20larger%20systemic%20issues%20in%20temple%20administration%20and%20has%20called%20for%20the%20sanctity%20of%20Hindu%20religious%20practices%20being%20protected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20began%20after%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20animal%20fat%20was%20used%20to%20make%20the%20sought-after%20laddoos%20given%20as%20'prasad'%20by%20the%20Sri%20Venkateswara%20Temple%20in%20Tirupati%20under%20the%20previous%20YSR%20Congress%20government.%20The%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20government%20then%20cited%20a%20report%20by%20a%20Gujarat%20laboratory%20which%20stated%20that%20the%20ghee%20used%20in%20the%20laddoos%20contained%20traces%20of%20beef%20tallow%2C%20fish%20oil%2C%20and%20lard%20(pig%20fat).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20petition%20sent%20to%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%2C%20lawyer%20Satyam%20Singh%20has%20said%20the%20allegations%20on%20the%20prasad%20at%20the%20temple%2C%20managed%20by%20the%20Tirumala%20Tirupati%20Devasthanams%20(TTD)%2C%20have%20hurt%20the%20sentiments%20of%20devotees%20and%20the%20alleged%20act%20of%20using%20animal%20fat%20in%20the%20laddoos%20violates%20Article%2025%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20which%20guarantees%20the%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20religion%2C%20including%20the%20right%20to%20practice%20religious%20customs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20several%20judgments%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20have%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20protecting%20essential%20religious%20practices%2C%20the%20petition%20claims%20the%20Tirupati%20incident%20is%20symptomatic%20of%20larger%20systemic%20issues%20in%20temple%20administration%20and%20calls%20for%20dedicated%20and%20culturally%20sensitive%20management%20of%20temples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20who%20has%20sent%20the%20letter%20has%20also%20sought%20the%20protection%20of%20Hindu%20religious%20practices%20and%20ensuring%20proper%20management%20of%20sacred%20institutions%2C%20and%20urged%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20intervention%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Friday%2C%20Union%20Health%20Minister%20JP%20Nadda%20asked%20Mr%20Naidu%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bdetailed%20report%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20allegations.%20The%20BJP%2C%20which%20is%20an%20ally%20of%20Mr%20Naidu's%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20and%20the%20Jana%20Sena%2C%20has%20said%20the%20alleged%20use%20of%20animal%20fat%20is%20an%20unforgivable%20sin%2C%20with%20senior%20leader%20Bandi%20Sanjay%20hinting%20that%20it%20may%20have%20happened%20because%20a%20%26quot%3Bfew%20people%20from%20other%20religions%20had%20been%20inducted%26quot%3B%20into%20the%20TTD%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Diversionary%20Tactics'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20YSR%20Congress%20and%20former%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20have%20rubbished%20the%20allegations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20statement%20on%20the%20controversy%20on%20Friday%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20said%20the%20claims%20were%20false%20and%20a%20diversionary%20tactic%20by%20the%20TDP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20YSR%20Congress%20leader%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20YV%20Subba%20Reddy%2C%20who%20was%20the%20TTD%20chairman%20for%20four%20years%2C%20accused%20Mr%20Naidu%20of%20damaging%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20Tirumala%20shrine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChandrababu%20Naidu%20has%20severely%20damaged%20the%20sanctity%20of%20Tirumala%20and%20the%20faith%20of%20crores%20of%20Hindus.%20His%20comments%20about%20the%20Tirumala%20prasad%20are%20extremely%20malicious.%20No%20person%20would%20speak%20such%20words%20or%20make%20such%20accusations%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Reddy%20had%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20proven%20again%20that%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20will%20stoop%20to%20any%20level%20for%20political%20gain.%20To%20strengthen%20the%20faith%20of%20the%20devotees%2C%20I%2C%20along%20with%20my%20family%2C%20am%20ready%20to%20take%20an%20oath%20before%20the%20almighty%20regarding%20the%20Tirumala%20'prasad'.%20Is%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20willing%20to%20do%20the%20same%20with%20his%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726827840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Fhn8pprq_tirupati-temple-getty_625x300_24_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Find