ressure%20levels%20in%20recent%20checkups.%20None%20of%20this%20is%20to%20the%20same%20degree%20as%20my%20mother's%20health%20issues%2C%20but%20I%20find%20it%20concerning%20nonetheless.%20I've%20also%20been%20prone%20to%20the%20same%20severe%20bouts%20of%20depression%20that%20she%20endured%20when%20she%20was%20alive.%20If%20we%20share%20all%20these%20other%20similarities%2C%20why%20not%20also%20an%20early%20death%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI've%20learned%20I'm%20not%20alone%20in%20how%20I%20feel.%20Searching%20through%20Reddit%20and%20other%20message%20boards%2C%20I%20found%20plenty%20of%20people%20who%20believe%20their%20time%20is%20running%20out.%20I%20began%20to%20think%20that%20maybe%20these%20feelings%20weren't%20so%20illogical%20after%20all%2C%20and%20I%20finally%20decided%20to%20research%20why%20I%20felt%20this%20way.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223a006f19-4779-4430-b007-aaf3c88cf2c8%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHer%20death%20doesn't%20mean%20anything%20about%20my%20own%20necessarily%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20irrational%2C%26quot%3B%20explains%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psychologytoday.com%2Fus%2Ftherapists%2Fjumoke-m-omojola-omaha-ne%2F264140%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EJumoke%20Omojola%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20psychotherapist%20who%20helps%20those%20dealing%20with%20grief%20and%20anxiety.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it's%20not%20a%20given%20that%20if%20your%20mom%20or%20dad%20died%20young%2C%20you're%20definitely%20going%20to%20die%20young.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPlenty%20of%20evidence%20proves%20certain%20diseases%20can%20be%20passed%20down%20from%20parent%20to%20child.%20According%20to%20the%20book%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fbooks%2FNBK19932%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAlthough%2520there%2520are%2520many%2520possible%2Cautoimmune%2520disorders%2C%2520and%2520psychiatric%2520illnesses.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGenes%2C%20Behavior%2C%20and%20the%20Social%20Environment%3A%20Moving%20Beyond%20the%20Nature%2FNurture%20Debate%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20published%20by%20the%20National%20Institutes%20of%20Health%2C%20%26quot%3Bfamily%20history%20is%20often%20one%20of%20the%20strongest%20risk%20factors%20for%20common%20disease%20complexes%20such%20as%20cancer%2C%20cardiovascular%20disease%2C%20diabetes%2C%20autoimmune%20disorders%2C%20and%20psychiatric%20illnesses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20this%20doesn't%20necessarily%20mean%20I%20will%20suffer%20the%20same%20fate%20as%20my%20mother.%20Individual%20physiology%2C%20lifestyle%2C%20and%20just%20plain%20luck%20also%20come%20into%20play.%20According%20to%20Omojola%2C%20my%20guilt%20plays%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20how%20I%20am%20feeling%2C%20and%20much%20of%20it%20stems%20from%20the%20sudden%20loss%20of%20connection%20we%20have%20when%20we%20lose%20someone%20close%20to%20us.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20caregiving%20and%20social%20structures%20change%2C%20we%20adjust%20in%20different%20ways.%20Sometimes%2C%20people%20engage%20in%20risky%20behaviors%20like%20excessive%20smoking%20and%20drinking%2C%20and%20others%20will%20let%20their%20minds%20run%20wild%2C%20wracked%20with%20guilt%20and%20grief.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BGuilt%20is%20there%20because%20our%20culture%20does%20not%20provide%20children%2C%20especially%20young%20ones%2C%20with%20the%20reason%20why%20their%20parents%20died%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20explains.%20%26quot%3BThey%20make%20up%20their%20own%20stories%20when%20they%20are%20not%20provided%20with%20appropriate%20information%20about%20their%20parents%20or%20death.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOmojola%20goes%20on%20to%20explain%20to%20me%20that%20by%20linking%20the%20death%20of%20my%20mother%20with%20my%20own%20health%20issues%2C%20I%20was%20correlating%20truly%20unrelated%20events%20and%20engaging%20in%20magical%20thinking.%20The%20way%20to%20overcome%20this%2C%20she%20says%2C%20is%20to%20keep%20challenging%20my%20assumptions.%20I%20need%20to%20look%20after%20my%20health%20and%20listen%20to%20my%20doctors.%20Soon%2C%20she%20says%2C%20I%20will%20begin%20to%20realize%20that%20just%20because%20my%20mother%20died%20young%20doesn't%20mean%20I%20will%2C%20too.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20I%20will%20probably%20never%20recover%20from%20the%20grief%20I%20still%20feel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-mom-died-young-im-worried-i-will-too-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726827182000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e88595d17aa3c7b2b321a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-mom-died-young-im-worried-i-will-too-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I'm%2046%2C%20which%20is%20almost%20the%20same%20age%20my%20mom%20was%20when%20she%20died.%20I'm%20worried%20I'll%20die%20young%2C%20too%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20see%20my%20kids%20grow%20up.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jason%20Keil)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-mom-died-young-im-worried-i-will-too-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Yudhra%20X%20review%3A%20Action-thriller%20gets%20mixed%20reactions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726827177000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113522696%2Cimgsize-36016.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fyudhra-twitter-review-siddhant-chaturvedis-action-thriller-receives-a-mixed-reactions%2Farticleshow%2F113522696.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cim