%5C%22%3EMy%20day%20in%20a%20nutshell%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20get%20up%20at%20about%206%20a.m.%20As%20soon%20as%20I%20wake%20up%2C%20I%20start%20prepping%20pastries%2C%20laying%20out%20the%20tables%2C%20and%20getting%20our%20guests%20coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20usually%20make%20a%20continental%20spread%20for%20breakfast%20with%20homemade%20granola%20yogurt%2C%20fruit%20plates%2C%20and%20pastries.%20Then%2C%20I'll%20have%20a%20hot%20option%20for%20the%20day%2C%20like%20eggs%20benedict%20or%20waffles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221260%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20dish%20made%20by%20Staddon.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66de7c845444ffafa7638a50%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22836%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20dish%20made%20by%20Staddon.%3Cp%3EMucho%20Gusto%20charter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20like%20cooking%20light%20and%20healthy%20food.%20So%20I%20do%20spreads%2C%20sometimes%20with%20homemade%20focaccia%2C%20and%20then%20a%20protein%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20guests'%20preferences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20try%20to%20source%20most%20of%20my%20produce%20from%20local%20farmers%20and%20fishermen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Staddon%20said%20she%20likes%20to%20cook%20light%2C%20healthy%20dishes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66de7cad5444ffafa7638a58%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStaddon%20said%20she%20likes%20to%20cook%20light%2C%20healthy%20dishes.%3Cp%3EMucho%20Gusto%20charter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELunches%20vary%20between%20plated%20salads%20and%20buffet-style%20courses.%20I%20whip%20up%20homemade%20ice%20cream%2C%20so%20there's%20always%20a%20selection%20available%20for%20dessert%20at%20lunch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20start%20prepping%20dinner%20at%20about%205%20p.m.%20and%20usually%20serve%20it%20at%20around%207%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20how%20active%20the%20guests%20have%20been%2C%20I%20may%20serve%20a%20little%20snack%20plate%20before%20dinner%2C%20like%20some%20fresh%20fruits%20or%20a%20charcuterie%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20about%207%20p.m.%2C%20once%20all%20the%20guests%20have%20showered%20and%20are%20ready%20for%20dinner%2C%20I'll%20have%20set%20the%20table.%20Dominic%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20serves%20sundown%20cocktails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnless%20guests%20request%20a%20lighter%20meal%2C%20we%20usually%20do%20three%20courses%20%E2%80%94%20starters%2C%20mains%2C%20and%20desserts.%20I've%20gotten%20good%20reviews%20for%20my%20sushi%20spreads%2C%20in%20particular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Staddon%20with%20her%20sushi%20platters.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66de7d085444ffafa7638a5e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStaddon%20said%20her%20sushi%20platters%20always%20get%20glowing%20reviews.%3Cp%3EMucho%20Gusto%20charter%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20homemade%20pasta%20is%20also%20generally%20a%20winner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20I%20make%20black%20pepper%20and%20truffle%20pasta%20with%20sauteed%20mushrooms%20and%20a%20big%20wagyu%20steak.%20People%20go%20nuts%20for%20that%2C%20so%20I%20must%20be%20doing%20something%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Staddon%20plating%20one%20of%20her%20main%20courses.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66de7df0a0ff598b2665aa0c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStaddon%20plating%20one%20of%20her%20main%20courses.%3Cp%3EMucho%20Gusto%20charter%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20an%20age%20limit%20of%2012%20on%20board%20the%20yacht.%20But%20at%20that%20age%2C%20many%20kids%20still%20have%20a%20limited%20palate%2C%20so%20food%20looks%20like%20chicken%20nuggets%20and%20chips%20or%20pizza%20all%20week.%20They%20generally%20only%20eat%20maybe%20two%20or%20three%20different%20meals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenerally%2C%20mums%20communicate%20their%20preferences%20to%20me.%20So%2C%20I%20ensure%20that%20chicken%20nuggets%20and%20chips%20are%20stocked%20on%20board%20and%20heat%20them%2020%20minutes%20before%20meals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20dessert%2C%20we%20clean%20up%2C%20stack%20the%20dishwasher%2C%20and%20prep%20for%20the%20next%20day.%20If%20I%20need%20to%20make%20focaccia%20dough%20or%20I'm%20doing%20cinnamon%20buns%20the%20next%20morning%2C%20I've%20got%20to%20make%20all%20the%20dough%20that%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20I%20can%20typically%20go%20to%20bed%2C%20which%20could%20be%20any%20time%20between%209%3A30%20p.m.%20and%2010%3A30%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2215f1d9d7-43b2-4e7c-bb15-6373baafdcc6%5C%22%3EBetter%20than%20other%20restaurant%20jobs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESomething%20I've%20enjoyed%20about%20the%20job%20is%20that%20I%20get%20to%20be%20a%20lot%20more%20involved%20with%20what's%20happening%20outside%20the%20kitchen%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20confined%20to%20working%20in%20a%20kitchen%20all%20day%2C%20you%20can%20feel%20detached%20from%20what%20happens%20outside%20it.%20And%20in%20a%20restaurant%20kitchen%2C%20you're%20often%20making%20the%20meal%20you've%20been%20told%20to%20make%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20getting%20to%20be%20creative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20different%20on%20a%20yacht.%20I%20get%20to%20understand%20the%20guests%20and%20build%20relationships%20with%20them.%20And%20that's%20my%20favorite%20part%20of%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-chef-luxury-yacht-british-virgin-islands-what-i-make-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726825856000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d95b7c5444ffafa7625a21%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22