y%2C%20it's%20feeling%20very%202021%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20for%20a%20chosen%20few.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22silicon%20valley%20VC%20speed%20funding%204x3%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60662e3852f11d0019431afb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221876%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESamantha%20Lee%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESuddenly%2C%20it's%20feeling%20very%20%26quot%3B2021%26quot%3B%20for%20tech%20companies%20with%20an%20AI%20story%20and%20a%20viable%20business%20model.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20startups%20are%20attracting%20rapid%20funding%20rounds%2C%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20doldrums%20of%20the%20overall%20market.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInvestors%20face%20pressure%20to%20secure%20stakes%20in%20top%20AI%20firms%2C%20risking%20inflated%20valuations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Glean%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-startups-most-promising-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%20a%20%24200%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20funding%20round%20valuing%20the%20AI%20enterprise%20software%20startup%20at%20%242.2%20billion.%20Normally%2C%20a%20founder%20would%20hop%20off%20the%20fundraising%20treadmill%20after%20such%20a%20close.%20But%20these%20are%20not%20normal%20times%2C%20and%20Glean%20has%20the%20kind%20of%20meteoric%20revenue%20growth%20that%20lights%20up%20the%20eyes%20of%20VCs%2C%20more%20than%20tripling%20annual%20recurring%20revenue%20over%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%20overnight%2C%20founder%20Arvind%20Jain's%20inbox%20filled%20up%20with%20cold%20emails%20from%20other%20investors%20%E2%80%94%20hungry%20for%20a%20piece%20of%20the%20startup%20unicorn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20kept%20telling%20people%20that%2C%20look%2C%20we%20just%20raised%2C%20we%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20capital%2C%20and%20we%20feel%20fine%2C%26quot%3B%20Jain%20said.%20He%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BBut%20then%20that%20inbound%20kept%20coming%20in%2C%20and%20at%20some%20point%20we%20said%2C%20OK%2C%20well%2C%20let's%20think%20about%20does%20it%20actually%20make%20sense%20for%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20month%2C%20Glean%20snagged%20another%20%24260%20million%20from%20investors%20such%20as%20Altimeter%20Capital%20and%20DST%20Global%2C%20in%20a%20deal%20that%20doubles%20its%20valuation%20to%20%244.6%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20transaction%20is%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20string%20of%20dizzying%20back-to-back%20funding%20rounds%20at%20ever-higher%20valuations%20for%20a%20handful%20of%20AI%20startups%20that%20stand%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20the%20doldrums%20of%20the%20overall%20market%20for%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20funding%20velocity%20for%20top%20AI%20startups%20is%20extremely%20rapid%20right%20now%2C%20with%20some%20raising%20multiple%20large%20rounds%20within%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Steve%20Brotman%2C%20founder%20and%20managing%20partner%20of%20Alpha%20Partners.%20%26quot%3BThis%20reflects%20the%20massive%20investor%20excitement%20and%20FOMO%20around%20AI%2C%20but%20also%20creates%20risks%20of%20inflated%20valuations%20and%20unrealistic%20expectations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20search%20company%20Perplexity%20secured%20%2462.7%20million%20in%20funding%20in%20April%2C%20less%20than%20four%20months%20after%20it%20raised%20%2473.6%20million%20in%20a%20Series%20B%20round.%20And%20the%20round%20may%20not%20be%20done%20yet.%20In%20June%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported%20that%20it's%20having%20discussions%20with%20SoftBank%20to%20invest%20at%20a%20%243%20billion%20valuation.%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20Perplexity%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20semiconductor%20company%20Groq%20is%20already%20exploring%20another%20funding%20round%20at%20a%20substantially%20higher%20valuation%20shortly%20after%20it%20locked%20up%20%24640%20million%20in%20a%20Series%20D%20round%20in%20August%2C%20according%20to%20two%20people%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20matter.%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20Groq%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESakana%20AI%2C%20a%20Tokyo-based%20AI%20research%20company%20founded%20by%20Google%20engineers%20in%202023%2C%20announced%20this%20month%20it%20raised%20a%20%24100%20million%20Series%20A%20funding%20round%20led%20by%20New%20Enterprise%20Associates%2C%20Khosla%20Ventures%20and%20Lux%20Capital.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Sakana%20raised%20%2430%20million%20in%20a%20seed%20funding%20round%20led%20by%20Lux%20Capital.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscoop-slingshot-ai-raises-30-million-a16z-menlo-follow-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESlingshot%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20built%20an%20automated%20mental%20health%20counselor%2C%20also%20raised%20separate%20rounds%20of%20funding%20just%20months%20apart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20happens%20after%20these%20rounds%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20don't%20get%20in%2C%20so%20there%20may%20be%20a%20billion%20dollars%20on%20the%20sidelines%20that's%20ready%20for%20the%20next%20round%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gregg%20Hill%2C%20cofounder%20of%20Parkway%20Venture%20Capital%2C%20which%20invested%20in%20Figure%20AI%2C%20a%20robotics%20company%20valued%20at%20%242.6%20billion.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that's%20also%20a%20reason%20why%20you%20see%20some%20of%20these%20rounds%20happening%20sooner%20than%20later.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2241d943c1-443d-4f86-aa1c-67788333b773%5C%22%3EThe%20have%20and%20have-nots%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pace%20at%20which%20these%20AI%20startups%20are%20raising%20fresh%20rounds%20of%20capital%20has%20created%20a%20new%20dichotomy%20among%20tech%20founders.%20Unlike%20the%20tech%20boom%20that%20ended%20in%202020%2C%20where%20companies%20from%20crypto%20to%20consumer%20were%20raising%20huge%20rounds%2C%20the%20fervor%20this%20time%20is%20much%20more%20concentrated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20have%20and%20have-not%20scenario%20right%20now%20where%20if%20you're%20an%20emerging%20AI%20company%2C%20despite%20maybe%20not%20having%20really%20proven%20much%20of%20anything%20from%20the%20standpoint%20of%20revenue%20or%20significant%20user%20traction%2C%20you%20might%20be%20able%20to%20get%20some%20wildly%20amazing%20valuation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Matt%20Murphy%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20Menlo%20Ventures.%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20you%20could%20be%20a%20%2450%20million%20business%20right%20now%20growing%20at%2040%25%2C%20and%20people%20might%20view%20you%20as%20uninteresting%20because%20you're%20not%20an%20AI%20company.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223479%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anthropic%20CEO%20Dario%20Amodei%20at%20the%202023%20TechCrunch%20Disrupt%20conference%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66eb301ed17aa3c7b2b3eb58%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222609%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDario%20Amodei%20is%20a%20former%20OpenAI%20employee%20turned%20chief%20executive%20officer%20of%20Anthropic.%3Cp%3EKimberly%20White%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20which%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20closest%20competitor%20to%20OpenAI%2C%20closed%20a%20%24750%20million%20funding%20round%20led%20by%20Menlo%20Ventures%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F02%2F20%2Ftechnology%2Fanthropic-funding-ai.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecapping%20a%20year%20where%20it%20raised%20a%20head%20spinning%20%247.3%20billion.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20firm's%20biggest%20ever%20check%2C%20and%20Murphy%20admits%20it%20felt%20%26quot%3Benormous.%26quot%3B%20But%20he%20says%20it%20felt%20justified%20given%20the%20company's%20rocketship%20trajectory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20one%20of%20those%20companies%20that%20I'd%20put%20in%20not%20that%2010%25%2C%20but%201%25%20category%20of%20year-over-year%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20Murphy%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20mind%20boggling.%20I've%20never%20seen%20that%20before.%20So%20they%20deserve%20some%20outsize%20premium.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic's%20%2418%20billion%20valuation%20also%20felt%20reasonable%20when%20compared%20to%20the%20%2486%20billion%20OpenAI%20reached%20around%20the%20same%20time%20in%20a%20deal%20that%20allowed%20some%20employees%20to%20sell%20stock.%20(OpenAI%20is%20now%20reportedly%20seeking%20a%20%24150%20billion%20valuation.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20scarcity%20factor%20of%20there's%20really%20only%20two%20places%20to%20invest%20if%20you%20want%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20heart%20and%20soul%20foundation%20large%20language%20models%20of%20this%20wave%2C%20and%20one's%20getting%20priced%20at%20a%20more%20than%20hundred%20billion%2C%26quot%3B%20Murphy%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhatever%20the%20other%20one%20is%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20there's%20probably%20more%20upside%20on%20the%20investment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2229f18fc9-a990-4a4a-b770-9b5552d45af7%5C%22%3EPressure%20to%20someday%20make%20money%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20for%20AI%20startups%2C%20the%20pressure%20is%20on%20to%20show%20investors%20that%20their%20businesses%20won't%20just%20burn%20cash%20but%20also%2C%20someday%2C%20make%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22938%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22AI%20robot%20artificial%20intelligence%20money%20hand%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66eb2f8bce3009a0fac76712%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22704%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Jenny%20Chang-Rodriguez%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Jain%2C%20a%20former%20Google%20engineer%20and%20cofounder%20of%20Rubrik%2C%20some%20of%20those%20startups%20that%20could%20raise%20money%20out%20the%20gate%20are%20now%20struggling%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20generate%20the%20amount%20of%20revenues%20required%20to%20provide%20a%20return%20on%20investment.%20%26quot%3BThey%20couldn't%20go%20beyond%20the%20proof%20of%20concept%20stage%20with%20their%20customers%20because%20ultimately%20they're%20not%20adding%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20Jain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20puts%20an%20inordinate%20amount%20of%20investor%20attention%2C%20and%20pressure%2C%20on%20those%20companies%20with%20business%20models%20that%20seem%20to%20be%20working.%20%26quot%3BSuddenly%2C%20we%20came%20into%20this%20environment%20where%20now%20there's%20a%20handful%20of%20AI%20companies%20that%20are%20actually%20generating%20meaningful%20revenue%2C%20driving%20meaningful%20user%20engagement%2C%20and%20adding%20business%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20Jain%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20we%20are%20one%20of%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJai%20Das%2C%20president%20and%20partner%20at%20Sapphire%20Ventures%2C%20said%20he%20and%20a%20partner%2C%20Rajeev%20Dham%2C%20looked%20at%20Glean%20during%20the%20last%20fundraise%20but%20couldn't%20get%20the%20votes%20to%20do%20the%20deal.%20By%20the%20time%20Glean%20went%20out%20to%20raise%20again%2C%20it%20had%20cruised%20past%20the%20sales%20projections%20that%20Das%20saw%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20year.%20In%20September%2C%20Sapphire%20joined%20the%20company's%20Series%20E%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGlean%20did%20not%20raise%20on%20a%20promise%2C%26quot%3B%20Das%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BGlean%20raised%20on%20actual%20execution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d8ca873b-024f-46b8-ae4f-6f4c09901585%5C%22%3ENew%20challenges%20for%20founders%20and%20VCs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20founders%20of%20hot%20AI%20companies%2C%20there%20are%20certainly%20worse%20problems%20to%20have%20than%20eager%20VCs%20pounding%20down%20the%20door%20trying%20to%20give%20you%20more%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20saying%20in%20VC%20that%20you%20raise%20money%20when%20you%20don't%20need%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hill.%20%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20best%20companies%20that%20ever%20came%20out%20of%20VC%2C%20like%20Uber%2C%20were%20always%20raising%20money%20because%20they%20were%20trying%20to%20disrupt%20a%20whole%20industry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%2C%20investors%20warn%20having%20too%20much%20cash%20can%20be%20just%20as%20detrimental%20as%20having%20too%20little%2C%20especially%20when%20companies%20have%20yet%20to%20achieve%20true%20product-market%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20understand%20for%20founders%20that%20oftentimes%20it%20could%20be%20tempting%20because%20you%20want%20to%20fortify%20your%20balance%20sheet%20and%20last%20for%2010%20years%20but%20sometimes%20it's%20not%20a%20good%20thing%20to%20last%20for%2010%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Murphy%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnytime%20you%20overcapitalize%20the%20company%2C%20I%20think%20there's%20just%20risk%20that%20a%20company%20gets%20sloppy%20or%20takes%20things%20for%20granted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDas%2C%20the%20Glean%20investor%2C%20said%20he%20never%20wants%20to%20tell%20an%20entrepreneur%20to%20turn%20down%20money%20because%20it's%20impossible%20to%20know%20if%20a%20cataclysmic%20event%20is%20around%20the%20corner.%20The%20coronavirus%20outbreak%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20froze%20funding%20to%20startups%20for%20the%20first%20few%20months.%20However%2C%20he%20warns%20founders%20that%20one%20of%20the%20dangers%20of%20raising%20too%20much%20money%20is%20spending%20it%20recklessly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20a%20fast-growing%20company%20and%20people%20believe%20in%20what%20you're%20doing%2C%20that%20is%20great%2C%26quot%3B%20Das%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20what%20happens%20is%20people%20get%20complacent%20when%20you%20raise%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20and%20you%20hire%20people%20without%20really%20paying%20attention%20to%20it.%20You%20do%20things%20that%20are%20not%20core%20to%20the%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20some%20founders%20are%20weary%20of%20the%20risks%20of%20raising%20fast%20follow-on%20rounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20founder%20of%20a%20stealth%2C%20vertical%20software%20startup%20said%20it%20took%20four%20months%20and%2076%20meetings%20to%20secure%20a%20seed%20round%20of%20funding%20for%20her%20company%2C%20which%20utilizes%20generative%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20this%20past%20spring.%20She%20asked%20for%20anonymity%20since%20the%20round%20hasn't%20been%20announced%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20she%20got%20the%20money%2C%20the%20founder%20hit%20the%20ground%20selling.%20That's%20when%20the%20cold%20emails%20started%20trickling%20in.%20Three%20or%20four%20partners%20at%20other%20firms%20reached%20out%20and%20told%20her%20that%20in%20the%20process%20of%20due%20diligence%20on%20some%20of%20her%20competitors%2C%20they%20had%20spoken%20to%20customers%20who%20said%20they%20were%20taking%20their%20business%20to%20her%20startup.%20Those%20investors%20became%20more%20interested%20in%20%3Cem%3Eher%3C%2Fem%3E%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20founder%20is%20being%20selective%20about%20which%20meetings%20she%20takes.%20She%20worries%20that%20if%20she%20pitches%20an%20investor%20who%20ends%20up%20passing%2C%20she%20will%20put%20a%20%26quot%3Bscarlet%20letter%26quot%3B%20on%20her%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20all%20talk%20to%20each%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20founder%20said%20of%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20funding%20frenzy%20has%20also%20made%20the%20venture%20capitalist's%20job%20harder%2C%20increasing%20pressure%20to%20get%20allocation%20in%20the%20hottest%20deals%20while%20not%20overpaying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20VCs%2C%20this%20environment%20requires%20being%20much%20more%20proactive%20and%20moving%20quickly%20when%20evaluating%20AI%20deals%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alpha%20Partners'%20Brotman.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20pressure%20to%20make%20faster%20decisions%20with%20less%20diligence.%20It%20also%20means%20needing%20to%20build%20stronger%20relationships%20with%20founders%20earlier%2C%20before%20companies%20are%20raising.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20if%20they%20manage%20to%20get%20into%20a%20hot%20company%2C%20maintaining%20their%20ownership%20stake%20is%20more%20challenging%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVCs%20are%20increasingly%20faced%20with%20frequent%20requests%20from%20their%20hot%20AI%20companies%20to%20follow%20on%20or%20double%20down%20on%20investments%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Iris%20Sun%2C%20an%20investor%20at%20500%20Global.%20%26quot%3BThis%20often%20leads%20to%20competition%20for%20pro-rata%20rights%2C%20with%20some%20companies%20implementing%20pay-to-play%20provisions.%20Failure%20to%20participate%20properly%20in%20these%20rounds%20can%20result%20in%20significant%20dilution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20other%20VCs%20say%20ultimately%20their%20job%20has%20not%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20no%20different%20than%20I've%20seen%20in%20the%20past%20for%20other%20hype%20cycles%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sri%20Chandrasekar%2C%20managing%20partner%20of%20Point72%20Private%20Investments.%20%26quot%3BMy%20job%20is%20to%20separate%20the%20hype%20from%20the%20reality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-startups-rapid-funding-rounds-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726822802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60702b1e4d3e410018b702bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-startups-rapid-funding-rounds-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Suddenly%2C%20it's%20feeling%20very%20%26quot%3B2021%26quot%3B%20for%20tech%20companies%20with%20an%20AI%20story%20and%20a%20viable%20business%20model.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bbergman%40insider.com%20(Ben%20Bergman%2CMelia%20Russell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A45%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-startups-rapid-funding-rounds-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3