tional%20Solicitor%20General%20SV%20Raju%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20federal%20agency%2C%20%26quot%3BMr%20Raju%2C%20what%20kind%20of%20grounds%20are%20taken%20in%20this%20plea%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20can%20you%20say%20this...%20how%20can%20you%20say%20'hostile%20atmosphere%20prevails%20in%20Bengal%20courts'%3F%20Your%20officers%20may%20not%20like%20the%20judicial%20officers%20but%20don't%20make%20such%20statements%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CBI%20was%20told.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20was%20warned%20of%20contempt%20of%20court%20proceedings%20but%20after%20Mr%20Raju%20apologised%2C%20and%20acknowledged%20the%20petition%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bloosely%20drafted%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20court%20allowed%20its%20withdrawal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fresh%20petition%20will%20be%20filed%2C%20Mr%20Raju%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20had%20been%20mandated%20by%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20to%20investigate%2C%20with%20help%20from%20a%20special%20police%20team%2C%20%26quot%3Bheinous%20crimes%20of%20rape%20and%20murder%26quot%3B%20and%20other%20complaints%20of%20violence%20after%20the%20results%20of%20the%202021%20election%20were%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Assembly%20poll%20saw%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20Trinamool%20Congress%20retain%20power%20despite%20a%20strong%20challenge%20from%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20but%20the%20election%20period%20and%20that%20after%20were%20marred%20by%20shocking%20reports%20of%20violence%20across%20the%20state%3B%20multiple%20videos%20and%20images%20of%20atrocities%2C%20that%20each%20party%20claimed%20had%20been%20perpetrated%20by%20the%20other%2C%20flooded%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%2C%20in%20its%20directions%2C%20had%20criticised%20the%20state%20police%20for%20not%20filing%20complaints%20when%20presented%20with%20possible%20major%20crimes%2C%20such%20as%20rape%20or%20murder%2C%20and%20sometimes%20displayed%20a%20%26quot%3Bpredetermined%20mindset%20to%20take%20a%20case%20in%20a%20particular%20direction%26quot%3B%2C%20apparently%20to%20favour%20the%20accused%20who%2C%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20were%20identified%20as%20workers%20or%20supporters%20of%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20welcomed%20the%20judgment%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bhistoric%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20vindication%20of%20its%20claims%2C%20while%20the%20Trinamool%20expressed%20unhappiness%20over%20the%20CBI%20being%20summoned.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726817100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F8hssvigo_supreme-court_625x300_08_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-news-today-bengal-post-poll-violence-case-in-supreme-court-cbi-how-can-you-say-top-court-scolds-cbi-over-bengal-post-poll-violence-plea-6608072%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%20rebuked%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20over%20the%20wording%20of%20a%20plea%20asking%20that%20cases%20related%20to%20violence%20after%20the%202021%20Bengal%20election%20be%20heard%20outside%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-news-today-bengal-post-poll-violence-case-in-supreme-court-cbi-how-can-you-say-top-court-scolds-cbi-over-bengal-post-poll-violence-plea-6608072%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20One%20Nation%20One%20Election%20(ONOE)%20Is%20Oh%20Noe!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fmt366k2o_one-nation-one-election_625x300_18_September_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20on%20Twitter%20say%20it%20like%20no%20other.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20rather%20amusing%20that%20One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%20abbreviates%20to%20ONOE%20-%20oh%20noe!%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Union%20Cabinet%20cleared%20the%20One%20Nation%20One%20Election%20(ONOE)%20proposal%2C%20legacy%20television%20channels%2C%20dutifully%2C%20complied%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20playbook.%20Distract%20from%20the%20real%20issues%3A%20unemployment%2C%20inflation%2C%20anti-federal%20policies%2C%20Manipur%2C%20a%20plummeting%20rupee%2C%20fuel%20prices%20not%20being%20cut%20despite%20a%20decline%20in%20global%20crude%20oil%20prices%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EJust%20Like%20The%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20very%20similar%20to%20when%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20was%20passed%20last%20year.%20The%20news%20stayed%20on%20primetime%2C%20tucking%20away%20the%20government's%20ineffectual%20handling%20of%20the%20Manipur%20crisis.%20These%20con%20jobs%20have%20a%20pattern.%20The%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20can%20only%20come%20into%20effect%20after%20the%20Census%20and%20delimitation%20exercise%20have%20been%20completed.%20So%2C%20the%20earliest%20that%20it%20can%20happen%20is%202034.%20The%20ONOE%20is%20another%20'Weapon%20of%20Mass%20Distraction'!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20my%20colleague%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20and%20eminent%20jurist%20P.%20Chidambaram%20pointed%20out%2C%20%26quot%3BONOE%20would%20require%20at%20least%20five%20constitutional%20amendments%26quot%3B.%20The%20High%20Level%20Committee%20(HLC)%20on%20ONOE%2C%20headed%20by%20a%20former%20President%2C%20recommended%2018%20amendments%20to%20the%20Constitution%20and%20other%20statutes%20of%20Union%20Territories%20having%20Legislative%20Assemblies.%20This%20would%20require%20a%20Constitution%20Amendment%20Bill%20to%20be%20passed%20in%20Parliament%2C%20with%20a%20special%20majority%20(a%20majority%20of%20the%20total%20membership%20of%20the%20House%20and%20a%20majority%20of%20not%20less%20than%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20members%20of%20the%20House%20present%20and%20voting).%20Daydreaming%20is%20a%20popular%20hobby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Article%20368(2)%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%20ratification%20by%20not%20less%20than%20half%20of%20the%20states%20will%20be%20required%20to%20carry%20out%20amendments%20to%20Article%20324A%20to%20facilitate%20simultaneous%20elections%20of%20Panchayats%20and%20Municipalities.%20Similarly%2C%20in%20order%20to%20have%20a%20Single%20Electoral%20Roll%2C%20an%20amendment%20to%20Article%20325%20is%20required.%20To%20implement%20this%20amendment%2C%20ratification%20by%20not%20less%20than%20half%20of%20the%20States%20would%20be%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20six%20reasons%20why%20ONOE%20is%20antithetical%20to%20federalism%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20March%201994%2C%20the%20S.R.%20Bommai%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%20case%2C%20a%20landmark%20in%20safeguarding%20Indian%20federalism%2C%20strengthened%20the%20autonomy%20of%20states%20within%20the%20Indian%20polity.%20Thirty%20years%20later%2C%20in%20March%202024%2C%20the%20HLC%20submitted%20its%20report%20on%20simultaneous%20elections.%20However%2C%20the%20committee's%20composition%20failed%20to%20reflect%20the%20federal%20nature%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20as%20it%20did%20not%20include%20a%20single%20Chief%20Minister%20or%20representative%20of%20states.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Terms%20of%20Reference%20(ToR)%20of%20the%20HLC%20are%2C%20in%20themselves%2C%20conclusive%20proof%20of%20the%20government's%20blatant%20disregard%20for%20federalism.%20The%20second%20ToR%20tasks%20the%20committee%20with%20the%20dubious%20mandate%20to%20%26quot%3Bexamine%20and%20recommend%20if%20amendments%20to%20the%20Constitution%20would%20require%20ratification%20by%20states%26quot%3B.%C2%A0Any%20constitutional%20amendment%20to%20implement%20simultaneous%20polls%20would%20directly%20impact%20the%20tenure%20of%20state%20assemblies%20and%20governments.%20Even%20the%20Law%20Commission%20in%202018%20had%20suggested%20that%20while%20such%20amendments%20might%20not%20fall%20strictly%20under%20the%20proviso%20to%20Article%20368(2)%2C%20the%20government%20should%20still%20seek%20ratification%20from%20at%20least%20half%20of%20the%20states%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20abundant%20caution.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20study%20conducted%20by%20IDFC%20Institute%20showed%20that%20there%20is%20a%2077%25%20possibility%20of%20voters%20voting%20for%20the%20same%20party%20at%20centre%20and%20states%20if%20simultaneous%20elections%20take%20place.%20The%20study%20analysed%20voting%20behaviour%20for%20four%20rounds%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20(1999%2C%202004%2C%202009%20and%202014)%20in%20states%20where%20the%20assembly%20elections%20coincided%20with%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20BJP%20government%2C%20predictably%2C%20seeks%20to%20homogenise%20electoral%20opinion%20across%20all%20facets%20of%20political%20and%20personal%20life.%20As%20the%201960s%2C%20particularly%201962%2C%20demonstrated%2C%20simultaneous%20elections%20can%20sway%20voting%20behaviour%20and%20sideline%20regional%20aspirations%20and%20state-level%20issues.%20In%20the%201962%20General%20Elections%2C%20the%20party%20that%20won%20at%20the%20Union%20swept%20the%20simultaneous%20State%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20Madras%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Assam.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20has%20struggled%20with%20the%20logistical%20complexities%20of%20conducting%20multi-phase%20elections.%20The%202019%20Jharkhand%20Assembly%20Elections%20were%20held%20in%20five%20phases%20and%20the%202021%20West%20Bengal%20Assembly%20Elections%20were%20held%20in%20eight%20phases.%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20across%20three%20states%20were%20held%20in%20seven%20phases%2C%20and%20even%20then%2C%20it%20took%2011%20days%20just%20to%20release%20the%20voter%20turnout%20data%20for%20Phase%201.%20And%20you%20are%20talking%20about%20conducting%20simultaneous%20polls!%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhy%20were%20the%20Maharashtra%20elections%20not%20announced%20along%20with%20elections%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%3F%20Here's%20why.%20The%20Maharashtra%20government%20announced%20the%20Ladki%20Bahin%20scheme%20in%20the%20budget%20this%20June.%20The%20first%20tranche%20reached%20the%20bank%20accounts%20of%20women%20in%20August%20and%20second%20tranche%20will%20reach%20beneficiaries%20mid-October.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20questions.%20The%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20in%20a%20detailed%20letter%20to%20the%20HLC%20in%20January%202024%2C%20asked%20how%20many%20state%20assemblies'%20terms%20would%20need%20to%20be%20curtailed%20or%20extended%20before%20implementation%20of%20ONOE%3F%20And%20once%20implemented%2C%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20a%20state%20assembly%20or%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20is%20dissolved%20before%20its%20five-year%20term%3F%20So%2C%20fresh%20elections%20will%20be%20held%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20term.%20This%20in%20itself%20is%20contrary%20to%20the%20very%20idea%20of%20ONOE.%20Oh%20Noe!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20MP%2C%20leads%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAdditional%20research%3A%20Anagha%2C%20Ayashman%20Dey.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726816740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fmt366k2o_one-nation-one-election_625x300_18_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fone-nation-one-election-oh-noe-6607979%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Under%20Article%20368(2)%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%20ratification%20by%20not%20less%20than%20half%20of%20the%20states%20will%20be%20required%20to%20carry%20o