2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Indian%20government%20is%20happy%20to%20take%20tax%20from%20us%20without%20ensuring%20the%20bare%20humane%20conditions%20to%20work.%E2%80%9D%20They%20(the%20government)%20don't%20help%20taxpayers%20when%20they%20are%20laid%20off%2C%20but%20would%20%E2%80%9Chappily%20collect%20the%20taxes%20from%20us%20when%20they%20aren't%20even%20giving%20us%20the%20basic%20necessities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLet%20this%20be%20the%20last%20death%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Ashare%3A7242079673730408450%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22641%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnAnna%20Sebastian%2C%20a%20consultant%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fey-india-work-stress-death-anna-sebastian-perayil-daughter-26-died-of-overwork-at-ey-no-one-attended-funeral-womans-letter-6595688%C2%A0%5C%22%3Edied%20four%20months%20after%20joining%20EY%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Her%20mother%2C%20Anita%20Augustine%2C%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20EY%20India's%20chairman%2C%20Rajiv%20Memani%2C%20accusing%20the%20company%20of%20fostering%20a%20culture%20that%20%26quot%3Bglorifies%20overwork.%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Augustine%20claimed%20that%20no%20one%20from%20EY%20attended%20her%20daughter's%20funeral%2C%20despite%20her%20death%20being%20linked%20to%20the%20company's%20demanding%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnna%2C%20who%20passed%20her%20Chartered%20Accountancy%20(CA)%20exams%20in%20late%202023%20and%20joined%20EY's%20Pune%20office%20in%20March%202024%2C%20had%20been%20struggling%20with%20anxiety%2C%20sleeplessness%2C%20and%20stress%20due%20to%20long%20work%20hours.%20Her%20mother%20described%20how%20Anna's%20enthusiasm%20for%20her%20first%20job%20quickly%20turned%20into%20an%20experience%20of%20exhaustion%20and%20pressure.%20Despite%20warni