ry%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726814520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F4pm85am_supreme-court-_625x300_17_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-courts-youtube-channel-hacked-6607678%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court's%20YouTube%20channel%20was%20hacked%20on%20Friday%20and%20showing%20videos%20promoting%20a%20cryptocurrency%20developed%20by%20US-based%20company%20Ripple%20Labs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-courts-youtube-channel-hacked-6607678%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWill%20Not%20Rest%20Until...%26quot%3B%3A%20EY%20Chief%20On%20Employee's%20Death%20Due%20To%20'Overwork'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIssuing%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20alleged%20death%20of%20a%2026-year-old%20employee%20because%20of%20'overwork'%2C%20Ernst%20%26amp%3B%20Young%20(EY)%20India%20Chairman%20Rajiv%20Memani%20has%20said%20the%20fact%20that%20no%20one%20from%20the%20company%20attended%20the%20funeral%20is%20alien%20to%20their%20culture%20and%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bwould%20not%20rest%26quot%3B%20until%20the%20objective%20of%20nurturing%20a%20harmonious%20workplace%20is%20accomplished.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Memani%20also%20said%20that%2C%20as%20a%20father%2C%20he%20could%20understand%20the%20anguish%20of%20the%20woman's%20mother%2C%20who%20had%20written%20a%20heartbreaking%20letter%20to%20him%2C%20and%20added%20that%20he%20has%20conveyed%20his%20deepest%20condolences%20to%20the%20family.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20letter%20to%20Mr%20Memani%2C%20Anita%20Augustine%2C%20the%20mother%20of%20Anna%20Sebastian%20Perayil%2C%20wrote%20that%20her%20daughter%20had%20died%20four%20months%20after%20joining%20EY's%20office%20in%20Pune%20and%20said%20the%20company's%20culture%20seemed%20to%20glorify%20overwork%20while%20neglecting%20the%20human%20beings%20behind%20the%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20posted%20on%20LinkedIn%20on%20Thursday%20night%2C%20Mr%20Memani%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20deeply%20saddened%20and%20as%20a%20father%2C%20I%20can%20only%20imagine%20Ms%20Augustine's%20grief.%20I%20have%20conveyed%20my%20deepest%20condolences%20to%20the%20family%2C%20although%20nothing%20can%20fill%20the%20void%20in%20their%20lives.%20I%20truly%20regret%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20missed%20being%20present%20at%20Anna's%20funeral.%20This%20is%20completely%20alien%20to%20our%20culture.%20It%20has%20never%20happened%20before%3B%20it%20will%20never%20happen%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EY%20India%20Chairman%20said%20he%20was%20aware%20that%20people%20had%20commented%20on%20some%20of%20the%20company's%20work%20practices%20on%20social%20media%20and%20emphasised%20that%20the%20company%20places%20the%20%26quot%3Bhighest%20importance%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20well-being%20of%20its%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20affirm%20that%20the%20well-being%20of%20our%20people%20is%20my%20top-most%20priority%20and%20I%20will%20personally%20champion%20this%20objective.%20I%20am%20absolutely%20committed%20to%20nurturing%20a%20harmonious%20workplace%2C%20and%20I%20will%20not%20rest%20until%20that%20objective%20is%20accomplished%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMother's%20Letter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Augustine%20wrote%20that%20Anna%20passed%20her%20chartered%20accountancy%20(CA)%20exams%20on%20November%2023%20last%20year%20and%20joined%20EY%20Pune%20on%20March%2019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20was%20full%20of%20life%2C%20dreams%2C%20and%20excitement%20for%20the%20future.%20EY%20was%20her%20first%20job%2C%20and%20she%20was%20thrilled%20to%20be%20part%20of%20such%20a%20prestigious%20company.%20But%20four%20months%20later%2C%20on%20July%2020th%2C%202024%2C%20my%20world%20collapsed%20when%20I%20received%20the%20devastating%20news%20that%20Anna%20had%20passed%20away.%20She%20was%20just%2026%20years%20old%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20anguished%20mother%20said%20that%20Anna's%20workload%20was%20so%20high%20that%20she%20had%20been%20complaining%20of%20chest%20constriction%20for%20a%20week%20after%20reaching%20her%20paying%20guest%20accommodation%20at%201%20am%20every%20day%20for%20a%20week%20and%20insisted%20on%20going%20to%20work%20even%20after%20seeing%20a%20doctor%2C%20saying%20she%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20tasks%20pending%20and%20would%20not%20get%20leave.%20Ms%20Augustine%20and%20her%20husband%20were%20visiting%20from%20Kochi%20at%20the%20time%20to%20attend%20Anna's%20CA%20convocation%2C%20but%20the%2026-year-old%20ended%20up%20being%20late%20even%20for%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20breaks%20my%20heart%20to%20tell%20you%20that%20even%20during%20those%20two%20days%2C%20which%20were%20the%20last%20we%20would%20spend%20with%20our%20child%2C%20she%20couldn't%20enjoy%20them%20because%20of%20the%20work%20pressure%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Augustine%20said%20no%20one%20from%20the%20company%20had%20attended%20Anna's%20funeral%2C%20which%20the%20family%20found%20deeply%20hurtful%20and%20added%20that%20she%20hoped%20that%20her%20letter%20would%20spark%20real%20change%20so%20that%20no%20other%20family%20has%20to%20endure%20what%20they%20went%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnna's%20father%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanna-sebastian-perayil-ey-india-getting-hardly-any-sleep-unable-to-eat-proper-food-ey-employees-father-6606677%5C%22%3Ehas%20also%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bgetting%20hardly%20any%20sleep%20and%20was%20unable%20to%20eat%20proper%20food%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20had%20called%20Anna's%2