tion%20near%20Odisha's%20Bhubaneswar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20cops%2C%20including%20an%20Inspector-rank%20officer%2C%20have%20been%20suspended%20pending%20a%20disciplinary%20procedure%20for%20%26quot%3Bgross%20misconduct%26quot%3B%2C%20Odisha%20Police%20HQ%20said%20hours%20after%20the%20alleged%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20has%20said%20she%20sought%20to%20file%20a%20complaint%20at%20the%20Bharatpur%20Police%20Station%20after%20she%20and%20her%20friend%20fought%20off%20a%20group%20of%20men%20who%20attacked%20them%20in%20public%20late%20Sunday%20night%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhen%20I%20(she%20was%20accompanied%20by%20her%20partner)%20was%20going%20home%20after%20closing%20my%20restaurant%20at%201%20am%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhen%20we%20reached%20the%20police%20station%20only%20a%20woman%20constable%20was%20there%2C%20in%20civil%20dress%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20she%20refused%20to%20help%20us%2C%20the%20Army%20officer's%20friend%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20woman%2C%20after%20the%20constable%20began%20verbally%20abusing%20her%2C%20a%20few%20more%20cops%2C%20male%20officers%20this%20time%2C%20arrived%20on%20the%20scene%20and%20asked%20her%20partner%20for%20a%20written%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20male%20policemen%20then%20allegedly%20threw%20the%20Army%20officer%20into%20a%20jail%20cell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20what%20happened...%20they%20put%20him%20in%20the%20lock-up.%20When%20I%20raised%20my%20voice%20to%20say%20they%20cannot%20put%20an%20Army%20officer%20in%20custody%20as%20it%20is%20unlawful%2C%20two%20female%20officers%20assaulted%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20claimed%2C%20adding%20she%20fought%20back%20and%20bit%20one%20of%20them%20but%20was%20overpowered%2C%20tied%20up%20with%20her%20jacket%2C%20and%20left%20in%20a%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20some%20time%2C%20a%20male%20officer%20opened%20the%20doors%20and%20kicked%20on%20my%20breasts%20several