%20Her%20Dad%3A%2022-YO%E2%80%99s%20Diabetes%20Insulin%20Carrier%20%E2%80%98Novocarry%E2%80%99%20Wins%20James%20Dyson%20Award%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EInsulin%20vials%20necessitate%20storing%20at%202%20to%208%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20beyond%20which%20the%20drug%20loses%20efficacy.%20And%20naturally%2C%20this%20prompted%20Indians%20to%20come%20up%20with%20some%20%3Cem%3Ejugaad%20%3C%2Fem%3E(also%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98innovative%20hacks%E2%80%99%20in%20local%20parlance)%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%20A%20few%20of%20them%20were%20Odisha%20native%20Komal%20Panda%E2%80%99s%20closest%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20a%20fourth-year%20student%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332593%2Fdesign-medical-devices-innovation-nid-harvard-student-save-lives-chennai-siddharth%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Institute%20of%20Design%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Komal%20(22)%20recently%20made%20headlines%20when%20she%20was%20announced%20the%20national%20winner%20of%20the%20prestigious%20James%20Dyson%20Award%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApplauding%20the%20ingenious%20tricks%20her%20friends%20devised%20to%20prolong%20the%20longevity%20of%20the%20insulin%20while%20travelling%2C%20she%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20them%20stores%20the%20vial%20in%20a%20thermos%20flask%2C%20while%20the%20other%2C%20who%20lives%20down%20South%20and%20makes%2027-hour-long%20train%20trips%20back%20home%2C%20purchases%20a%20chilled%20bottle%20of%20water%20at%20every%20station%20in%20which%20she%20then%20places%20the%20vial.%E2%80%9D%20Think%20of%20it%20like%20a%20mini-fridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClever%20as%20these%20innovations%20are%2C%20it%20baffled%20Komal%20how%20no%20one%20was%20finding%20the%20process%20cumbersome.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20had%20to%20be%20a%20simpler%20solution%E2%80%9D%2C%20she%20caught%20herself%20thinking%20this%20during%20one%20%E2%80%98Technically%20Complex%20Project%E2%80%99%20le