rrace-how-to-grow-farmer-buy-shipping-method-water-nurse-kerala-home-gardening-san196%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elotus%20entrepreneur%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20mastering%20the%20art%20of%20propagating%20these%20exotic%20flora.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBlossoming%20hobby%20into%20a%20business%20endeavour%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELathika%E2%80%99s%20love%20for%20gardening%20dates%20back%20to%20her%20childhood%2C%20where%20nurturing%20and%20witnessing%20the%20growth%20of%20plants%20brought%20her%20immense%20joy.%20%E2%80%9CEver%20since%20I%20was%20a%20kid%2C%20I%20enjoyed%20gardening%20and%20I%20used%20to%20derive%20happiness%20just%20by%20seeing%20these%20lotus%20blossoms%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20went%20on%20to%20become%20a%20primary%20government%20school%20teacher%20in%20her%20early%2020s%2C%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20resist%20herself%20from%20following%20her%20passion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20she%20delved%20into%20commercialising%20her%20water%20lilies%20and%20lotus%20plants.%20Started%20initially%20as%20a%20hobby%2C%20this%20intrinsic%20passion%20led%20her%20to%20transition%20from%20teaching%20to%20pursuing%20her%20green-thumb%20ambition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVenturing%20into%20uncharted%20territory%2C%20Lathika%20embarked%20on%20a%20quest%20to%20uncover%20and%20research%20the%20diverse%20world%20of%20lotus%20flowers%20and%20water%20lilies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20found%20that%20there%20were%20a%20hundred%20varieties%20of%20lotus%20and%20water%20lilies%20but%20out%20of%20these%2C%20only%20a%20few%20varieties%20were%20available%20in%20India.%20The%20rest%20were%20imported%20from%20countries%20such%20as%20Thailand%2C%20Vietnam%20and%20Japan%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2