%2F09%2FLeh-Groundwater-Image-4-1-1726234320.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22We%20are%20dealing%20with%20a%20broken%20sewage%20system%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Groundwater-Image-4-1-1726234320.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Groundwater-Image-4-1-1726234320-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Groundwater-Image-4-1-1726234320-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Groundwater-Image-4-1-1726234320-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Groundwater-Image-4-1-1726234320-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365904%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELeh%E2%80%99s%20sewage%20system%20is%20a%20significant%20problem%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20quality%20of%20its%20groundwater%20(Image%20courtesy%20Shutterstock%2F%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fg%2FOliverFoerstner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOliver%20Foerstner%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20study%20has%20revealed%20elevated%20levels%20of%20nitrates%2C%20faecal%20coliform%20bacteria%2C%20and%20other%20contaminants%20in%20many%20groundwater%20samples%2C%20indicating%20the%20impact%20of%20sewage%20infiltration.%20These%20contaminants%20pose%20serious%20health%20risks%2C%20especially%20to%20children%20and%20the%20elderly%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20local%20administration%20has%20taken%20some%20steps%20to%20address%20the%20issue%2C%20such%20as%20promoting%20the%20construction%20of%20improved%20septic%20tanks%20and%20encouraging%20the%20use%20of%20eco-friendly%20toilets%2C%20these%20measures%20have%20been%20insufficient%20to%20keep%20pace%20with%20the%20growing%20challenges%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20increased%20demand%20for%20water%20due%20to%20population%20growth%20and%20tourism%20puts%20additional%20pressure%20on%20our%20groundwater%20resources.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20more%20water%20is%20extracted%20from%20the%20aquifers%2C%20the%20natural%20recharge%20process%20is%20unable%20to%20keep%20pace%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20decline%20in%20groundwater%20levels%20and%20potential%20depletion%20of%20our%20aquifers%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGroundwater%20extraction%20in%20Leh%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiwaponline.com%2Fjwcc%2Farticle%2F15%2F4%2F1459%2F100946%2FGroundwater-scenario-under-climate-change-and%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20recent%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20April%202024%20in%20the%20Journal%20of%20Water%20and%20Climate%20Change%20led%20by%20Dr%20Farooq%20Ahmad%20Dar%20%E2%80%94%20assistant%20professor%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Geography%20and%20Disaster%20Management%2C%20University%20of%20Kashmir%20%E2%80%94%20groundwater%20extraction%20and%20decline%20in%20Leh%20has%20increased%20significantly%20in%20recent%20years.%20Here%20are%20two%20key%20data%20points%20from%20the%20study%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Well%20drilling%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%201997%2C%20there%20were%20only%2010%20drilled%20wells%20in%20Leh.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBy%202020%2C%20the%20total%20number%20of%20wells%20had%20grown%20to%202%2C659.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThis%20represents%20an%20increase%20of%20about%20115%20new%20wells%20per%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Groundwater%20extraction%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGroundwater%20extraction%20increased%20by%20approximately%2026%25%20from%202009%20to%202020.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAbout%20seven%20million%20cubic%20metres%20of%20water%20are%20drawn%20annually%20from%20wells.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Dr%20Dar%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20figures%20should%20raise%20alarm%20bells%20in%20the%20region.%20In%20simple%20language%2C%20these%20figures%20highlight%20the%20current%20scenario%20of%20groundwater%20pumping.%20When%20more%20people%20will%20shift%20to%20groundwater%20and%20drill%20their%20own%20wells%2C%20there%20will%20be%20no%20check%20on%20the%20reserves.%20Groundwater%20is%20a%20State%20Subject%20and%20that%20means%20it%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20local%20administration%20to%20have%20legal%20checks%20on%20its%20use%20and%20misuse.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20scenario%2C%20when%20more%20wells%20will%20be%20drilled%2C%20which%20we%20estimated%20at%20a%20rate%20of%20115%20wells%20per%20year%20(these%20figures%20are%20based%20on%20limited%20data%2C%20the%20rate%20could%20be%20even%20higher)%2C%20the%20reserves%20will%20be%20depleted%20very%20rapidly%20and%20the%20drilled%20wells%20will%20also%20fail%2Fdry%20out.%20This%20will%20have%20severe%20consequences%20on%20irrigation%2C%20tourism%2C%20industries%2C%20agriculture%20and%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives.%20So%2C%20the%20Government%20must%20intervene%20urgently%20to%20address%20this%20problem%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Town-5-1726235100.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Town-5-1726235100.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Town-5-1726235100-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Town-5-1726235100-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Town-5-1726235100-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Town-5-1726235100-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365922%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20people%20of%20Leh%20can%20no%20longer%20ignore%20the%20rapidly%20declining%20quality%20and%20quantity%20of%20their%20groundwater%20(Photo%20courtesy%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpixahive.com%2Fphoto%2Fmarket-place-at-leh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20PixaHive%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Population%20growth%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20population%20of%20the%20Ladakh%20region%20grew%20from%2029%2C730%20in%201901%20to%201%2C52%2C175%20in%202020.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThis%20represents%20an%20annual%20growth%20rate%20of%2015%25.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Urbanisation%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20built-up%20area%20increased%20by%2020%25%20from%201969%20to%202017.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20the%20built-up%20area%20around%20major%20towns%20increased%20by%20about%2075%25.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Glacier%20shrinkage%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGlaciers%20in%20the%20region%20have%20shrunk%20by%2040%25%20in%20area%20and%2025%25%20in%20volume%20since%20around%201650%20AD.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThis%20reduces%20the%20glacier%20melt%20that%20replenishes%20groundwater.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20study%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20provide%20specific%20measurements%20of%20groundwater%20level%20decline%2C%20it%20states%20that%20these%20factors%20have%20led%20to%20an%20imbalance%20between%20water%20demand%20and%20supply%2C%20decline%20of%20shallow%20resources%2C%20reduction%20of%20natural%20discharge%2C%20drying%20of%20springs%2C%20and%20decline%20in%20water%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWithout%20immediate%20intervention%2C%20the%20quality%20and%20quantity%20of%20Leh%E2%80%99s%20groundwater%20will%20continue%20to%20decline%20rapidly%20over%20the%20next%2020%E2%80%9330%20years.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20countdown%20we%20cannot%20ignore%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Chorol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESolutions%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20actionable%20solutions%20that%20the%20local%20government%2C%20administration%2C%20business%20owners%2C%20and%20residents%20can%20take%20to%20address%20the%20growing%20concern%20surrounding%20groundwater.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1)%20Stricter%20regulations%20for%20groundwater%20extraction%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Mandatory%20permits%20for%20groundwater%20extraction%3B%20metering%20of%20groundwater%20usage%3B%20pricing%20of%20groundwater%3B%20strict%20zoning%20regulations%3B%20establish%20clear%20guidelines%20on%20the%20minimum%20distance%20between%20borewells%20and%20septic%20tanks%3B%20hefty%20fines%20for%20businesses%20found%20dumping%20waste%20in%20water%20bodies%3B%20and%20regular%20mapping%20of%20groundwater%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2)%20Upgrading%20and%20improving%20Leh%E2%80%99s%20sewage%20management%20system%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Establish%20a%20decentralised%20sewage%20treatment%20plan%20with%20small-scale%20treatment%20systems%3B%20install%20advanced%20septic%20systems%20and%20dry%20toilets%20and%20composting%20systems%3B%20upgrade%20existing%20STPs%20and%20construct%20ne