er%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359581%2Finspiring-senior-citizens-india-running-successful-startups-isro-restaurants-oil-business-daycares%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehome-cooked%20specialties%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20across%20the%20country.%20From%20Uma%20Suresh%E2%80%99s%20prawn%20pickles%20in%20Kerala%20to%20Bhavana%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Enankhatais%20%3C%2Fem%3E(biscuits)%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Annie%20Philip%E2%80%99s%20matured%20plum%20cake%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Tocco%20is%20a%20melting%20pot%20of%20regional%20delicacies!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20women%20can%20be%20found%20everywhere%20%E2%80%94%20you%20just%20need%20to%20look%20and%20spend%20a%20few%20minutes%20talking%20to%20them.%20Ask%20your%20mother%20or%20aunt%20about%20their%20wishes%2C%20and%20if%20they%20are%20anything%20like%20Bhavana%20or%20Uma%2C%20they%20would%20have%20definitely%20harboured%20dreams%20of%20creating%20their%20own%20identity%20through%20cooking.%20Tocco%20makes%20it%20easy%20for%20neighbourhood%20home%20chefs%20to%20do%20just%20that%2C%20without%20the%20hassle%20of%20branding%20or%20marketing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20for%20this%20platform%20was%20born%20from%20founder%20Reshma%20Suresh%E2%80%99s%20own%20desire%20to%20experience%20the%20taste%20of%20home%20while%20living%20away.%20After%20moving%20to%20Mumbai%20for%20work%2C%20she%20found%20herself%20caught%20in%20the%20cycle%20of%20eating%20outside%2C%20always%20craving%20her%20%3Cem%3Eamma%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20tasty%20food.%20Realising%20she%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20one%20looking%20for%20authentic%20Kerala%20food%2C%20she%20started%20making%20banana%20chips%20and%20selling%20them%20through%20her%20brand%2C%20%E2%80%98MeenGurry%20Memories%E2%80%99%2C%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPacking%20memories%20of%20her%20%3Cem%3Eamma%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Eammamma%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fem%3E(grandmother%E2%80%99s)%20generations-old%20recipe%20for%20the%20perfect%2C%20thin%2C%20and%20crispy%20banana%20chips%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20game-changer%20for%20Reshma%2C%20who%20was%20then%20working%20at%20an%20AI%2Fhealthcare%20startup.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-1726037828-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tocco%20chef%20Annie%20baking%20a%20plum%20cake.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-1726037828-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-1726037828-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-1726037828-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-1726037828-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-1726037828-150x200.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-1726037828.jpeg%20960w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365472%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETocco%20chef%20Annie%20baking%20a%20plum%20cake.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20passion%20project%20soon%20took%20on%20a%20life%20of%20its%20own%20when%20she%20introduced%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20prawn%20and%20mango%20pickle.%20Rather%20than%20making%20the%20food%20herself%2C%20Reshma%20decided%20to%20create%20a%20platform%20where%20people%20like%20her%20mother%20and%20aunt%20could%20sell%20their%20dishes%20directly.%20This%20would%20help%20them%20become%20financially%20independent%20and%20turn%20their%20passion%20into%20a%20thriving%20business.%20For%20customers%2C%20it%20offers%20a%20way%20to%20enjoy%20the%20local%20delicacies%20they%20crave!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarted%20in%202023%2C%20Tocco%20now%20has%20over%2016%20chefs%2C%20both%20men%20and%20women%2C%20mostly%20in%20their%2050s%2C%20whose%20dreams%20have%20been%20given%20wings%20through%20the%20platform!%20Starting%20with%20just%20Rs%205%2C000%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355942%2Forganic-masala-spices-in-coimbatore-tamil-nadu-iniya-organics-business-podis-health-mixes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebootstrapped%20business%20%3C%2Fa%3Eachieved%20a%20turnover%20of%20over%20Rs%201%20crore%20in%20the%20current%20year.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20how%20Reshma%20is%20empowering%20those%20with%20a%20lifelong%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPacking%20childhood%20memories%20in%20a%20box%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReshma%2C%20an%20engineer%2C%20moved%20to%20Mumbai%20in%202012%20for%20work.%20She%20worked%20in%20healthcare%20startups%20for%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20gaining%20first-hand%20experience%20in%20healthcare%20and%20health%20tech.%20Joining%20these%20startups%20from%20their%20infancy%2C%20she%20had%20a%20front-row%20understanding%20of%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20scale%20a%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusy%20with%20work%2C%20a%20huge%20portion%20of%20her%2020s%20was%20spent%20eating%20out%20or%20cooking%20for%20herself.%20She%20constantly%20craved%20a%20good%20home-cooked%20meal%2C%20just%20like%20the%20ones%20her%20mother%20used%20to%20make.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20missed%20my%20roots%20and%20the%20food%20I%20grew%20up%20eating.%20Every%20time%20I%20visited%20home%20in%20Kochi%2C%20I%20brought%20back%20staples%20like%20banana%20chips%2C%20pickles%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Epodis%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spice%20powders)%2C%20whi