f%20Kerala.%20Long%20discussions%20between%20the%20sisters%20led%20to%20Reshma%20creating%20experience%20boxes%20in%202021%2C%20offering%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353263%2Fphilos-pickles-kerala-delivery-india-how-to-start-a-homemade-pickle-business-tips-tincy-thomas%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20Kerala%20meals%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20weekends.%20Prepared%20in%20her%20Mumbai%20kitchen%2C%20one%20dish%20clearly%20stood%20out%20%E2%80%94%20the%20banana%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20she%20decided%20to%20sell%20these%20chips%20under%20her%20venture%20%E2%80%98MeenGurry%20Memories%E2%80%99%20(%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Emeen%20gurry%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20means%20fish%20curry)%2C%20as%20a%20homage%20to%20their%20shared%20memories%20around%20the%20dining%20table.%20Every%20weekend%2C%20she%20curated%20different%20meal%20boxes%20while%20continuing%20her%20job%20during%20the%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20running%20MeenGurry%20Memories%2C%20Reshma%20realised%20that%20it%20was%20important%20to%20do%20something%20to%20promote%20chefs%20like%20her%20mother%20Uma%20and%20aunt%20Lakshmi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.29.28-1726037840-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Reshma%20with%20her%20freshly%20made%20banana%20chips%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.29.28-1726037840-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.29.28-1726037840-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.29.28-1726037840-768x102